These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-1::.
The people have 6 different jobs:  chef, entrepreneur, bartender, coach, project-manager, librarian
There are 6 different nationalities: thai, german, brazilian, australian, nigerian, french
1. the coach is on the left of the bartender##1
2. the german is on the left of the librarian##1
3. the chef is on the left of the entrepreneur##1
4. the nigerian is between the librarian and the thai##2
5. the australian is between the nigerian and the german##2
6. the thai is the coach##1
7. the project-manager is on the left of the thai##1
8. the french is on the left of the entrepreneur##1
9. the project-manager is on the right of the librarian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |       3       |       4        |    5     |   6    |
| Job           | chef | entrepreneur | librarian | project-manager | coach    | bartender  |
| Nationality   | french | german   | australian       | nigerian        | thai | brazilian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-2::.
There are 6 different nationalities: indonesian, brazilian, egyptian, mexican, pakistani, polish
6 different pets are kept: fish, cat, mouse, hamster, ferret, hedgehog
1. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
2. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the pakistani##1
3. the owner of the hamster is between the mexican and the indonesian##2
4. the egyptian is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
5. the indonesian is on the far right##1
6. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
7. the mexican is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
8. the brazilian is on the left of the polish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |  3   |    4    |   5    |     6      |
| Nationality   | brazilian | polish | pakistani | mexican | egyptian | indonesian  |
| Pet           | hedgehog | ferret  | fish | cat    | hamster  | mouse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-3::.
6 different pets are kept: lizard, fish, mouse, hedgehog, cat, ferret
The people use 6 different means of transport: subway, boat, trike, motorbike, bike, roller
1. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
2. the owner of the hedgehog is the person driving the bike##1
3. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
4. the person driving the subway is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
5. the owner of the mouse is on the far right##1
6. the owner of the cat is between the owner of the hedgehog and the person driving the subway##2
7. the person driving the boat is on the far left##1
8. the person driving the trike is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
9. the owner of the fish is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |     3      |   4    |     5      |     6     |
| Pet         | fish | lizard | ferret      | cat | hedgehog | mouse      |
| Transport   | boat    | roller  | subway | motorbike   | bike       | trike |

