.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-4::.
There 6 different types of food: apple, avocado, raspberry, kiwi, cranberry, pear
The people use 6 different means of transport: skateboard, jet-ski, car, van, bus, helicopter
1. the person driving the car is the person eating kiwi##1
2. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
3. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person eating raspberry##1
4. the person driving the van is the person eating avocado##1
5. the person eating apple is the person driving the skateboard##1
6. the person driving the jet-ski is between the person driving the skateboard and the person eating pear##2
7. the person eating avocado is on the left of the person eating pear##1
8. the person driving the car is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4     |   5    |   6    |
| Food        | avocado    | pear | raspberry | apple | cranberry | kiwi   |
| Transport   | van | bus        | jet-ski  | skateboard     | helicopter  | car |

