.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-5::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: documentary, animation, spy, adventure, comedy, crime
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: swimming, cricket, baseball, rowing, sailing, rugby
1. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
2. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
3. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
4. the person watching animation movies is between the person watching spy movies and the person watching comedy movies##2
5. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
6. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
7. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
8. the person watching comedy movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3    |   4    |   5   |    6     |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary   | adventure    | crime | spy | animation | comedy   |
| Sport         | sailing | swimming | baseball | rugby | rowing  | cricket |

