.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-6::.
There 6 different types of food: carrot, pear, cranberry, banana, lemon, corn
The people have 6 different hobbies: baking, filmmaking, rock-climbing, puzzles, magic-tricks, hiking
1. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is the person eating pear##1
3. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person eating lemon##1
4. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the far right##1
5. the person eating pear is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
6. the person eating corn is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
7. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the person eating corn##1
8. the person eating cranberry is between the person eating banana and the person who's hobby is hiking##2
9. the person eating carrot is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |    3    |      4      |     5     |      6      |
| Food    | carrot | corn | lemon  | banana      | cranberry | pear  |
| Hobby   | filmmaking  | rock-climbing    | puzzles | baking | magic-tricks | hiking |

