4. the person who's hobby is collecting is the person driving the taxi##1
5. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
6. the person who's hobby is puzzles is between the person driving the subway and the person driving the car##2
7. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
8. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
9. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1

.:: Answer ::.
