.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-8::.
The people have 6 different jobs:  dancer, security-guard, electrician, entrepreneur, architect, coach
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: house, classical, dubstep, folk, reggae, country
1. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the fan of folk##1
2. the fan of folk is on the left of the fan of classical##1
3. the fan of country is between the fan of reggae and the fan of house##2
4. the entrepreneur is the fan of dubstep##1
5. the electrician is between the security-guard and the architect##2
6. the fan of house is on the left of the fan of country##1
7. the architect is on the right of the coach##1
8. the architect is on the right of the coach##1
9. the electrician is on the right of the fan of classical##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |       3       |    4     |     5      |    6     |
| Job           | entrepreneur | coach | architect | electrician | security-guard | dancer |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep   | folk   | classical         | house    | country     | reggae     |

