.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-9::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: drawing, cooking, rock-climbing, board-games, collecting, baking
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: parkour, climbing, weightlifting, tennis, ice-hockey, badminton
 1. the person who's hobby is baking is the person who's sport is tennis##1
 2. the person who's sport is parkour is between the person who's hobby is drawing and the person who's sport is badminton##2
 3. the person who's sport is climbing is on the far left##1
 4. the person who's sport is tennis is the person who's hobby is baking##1
 5. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
 6. the person who's sport is tennis is the person who's hobby is baking##1
 7. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
 8. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 9. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
10. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2     |     3      |   4    |   5    |       6       |
| Hobby   | drawing   | collecting  | cooking | board-games | baking | rock-climbing     |
| Sport   | climbing | parkour | badminton    | ice-hockey | tennis | weightlifting |

