.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-10::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: martial-arts, sports, animation, crime, superhero, mystery
6 different pets are kept: hedgehog, frog, hamster, goat, dog, guinea-pig
1. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
2. the owner of the frog is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
3. the person watching superhero movies is the owner of the dog##1
4. the person watching martial-arts movies is the owner of the frog##1
5. the person watching martial-arts movies is between the person watching crime movies and the person watching sports movies##2
6. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
7. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
8. the person watching mystery movies is between the person watching crime movies and the owner of the hedgehog##2
9. the person watching superhero movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3     |   4    |      5      |   6    |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | mystery | crime   | martial-arts | sports | superhero |
| Pet           | hedgehog  | goat   | hamster | frog | guinea-pig       | dog |

