.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-11::.
6 different pets are kept: rat, hamster, horse, ferret, fish, mouse
The people use 6 different means of transport: bike, motorbike, ship, airplane, snowmobile, taxi
 1. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
 2. the owner of the fish is the person driving the snowmobile##1
 3. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
 4. the person driving the taxi is on the far right##1
 5. the person driving the snowmobile is between the person driving the motorbike and the owner of the horse##2
 6. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
 7. the person driving the bike is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
 8. the owner of the ferret is the person driving the bike##1
 9. the owner of the rat is between the person driving the bike and the owner of the hamster##2
10. the owner of the ferret is the person driving the bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2    |     3      |    4     |   5    |     6      |
| Pet         | mouse   | fish | horse       | ferret | rat    | hamster |
| Transport   | motorbike | snowmobile  | ship | bike      | airplane | taxi        |

