.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-12::.
The people have 6 different jobs:  social-worker, designer, accountant, dressmaker, freelancer, security-guard
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: action, superhero, crime, zombie, satire, documentary
 1. the accountant is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
 2. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
 3. the designer is the person watching zombie movies##1
 4. the accountant is between the dressmaker and the person watching documentary movies##2
 5. the person watching crime movies is between the person watching documentary movies and the freelancer##2
 6. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the social-worker##1
 7. the designer is on the far left##1
 8. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the social-worker##1
 9. the person watching documentary movies is the social-worker##1
10. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |         3          |      4      |    5    |      6       |
| Job           | designer      | dressmaker | accountant | social-worker   | security-guard  | freelancer |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | action  | superhero             | documentary | crime | satire       |

