.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-16::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, hot-chocolate, lemonade, 7up, milk, iced-tea
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: lacrosse, rugby, weightlifting, climbing, golf, skateboarding
1. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
3. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
4. the person who's sport is climbing is between the person who's sport is golf and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2
5. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
6. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the far left##1
7. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
8. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |      3       |   4    |     5      |    6    |
| Beverage   | milk   | soy-milk   | lemonade        | hot-chocolate   | iced-tea        | 7up   |
| Sport      | lacrosse | golf | climbing | weightlifting | skateboarding | rugby |

