.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-20::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: gardening, puzzles, sudoku, skydiving, filmmaking, hiking
There are 6 different nationalities: thai, french, german, polish, egyptian, brazilian
 1. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 2. the thai is on the far left##1
 3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 4. the polish is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 5. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far right##1
 6. the brazilian is on the right of the polish##1
 7. the french is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 8. the egyptian is on the right of the thai##1
 9. the german is between the person who's hobby is hiking and the person who's hobby is gardening##2
10. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |     3      |      4      |       5       |    6    |
| Hobby         | skydiving | gardening | puzzles | hiking | filmmaking | sudoku |
| Nationality   | thai | egyptian | german      | polish     | brazilian       | french |

 